text: Haplolobus leenhoutsii is a species of plant in the Burseraceae family. It is endemic to Borneo where it is confined to Sarawak. The species epithet, leenhoutsii, honours Pieter Willem Leenhouts. pdf ==References== leenhoutsii Category:Endemic flora of Borneo Category:Flora of Sarawak Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
